{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am now in charge with another person in charge of the wives of the Jewish elders of the prominence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what do we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are going out to an orchard and cleaning up and harvesting the fruits and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm-- and this is-- by that time, the apples are getting greener and the pears and everything-- I-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, this is heaven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We march out every day, they-- they lock us into the orchard, and the guard disappears.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed there all day and we eat fruit like you couldn't believe, right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now, this is already the middle of '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we know things are happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day, we see thousands of planes-- American planes go over, towards the big factories in Czechoslovokia, the Skoda factories, the armament factories.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we know the Allies have landed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we always used to say, god damn it why do the English drink tea all the time?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They should be here faster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things are happening on the Russian front, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We hear about Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We hear all these things, you now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans got kicked out of Africa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're not-- we're not having a paper, but word gets out, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So now they're getting ready for an inspection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was a Red Cross inspection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And right after that, a Danish and Swedish inspection, right, because the Danish Red Cross wants to see how their prisoners are treated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, if you were at the Yad Vashem and you went upstairs where all these-- the signs are, you come to Denmark, and it says 77 people died, right?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we lost 77 people in that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they basically starved to death, they were, you know, elderly people and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
